<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Frozen_error on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/frozen_error/</link><description>Recent content in Frozen_error on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/frozen_error/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Ruby FrozenError — Can't Modify Frozen Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/frozen-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/frozen-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="frozenerror--cant-modify-frozen-fix"&gt;FrozenError — Can&amp;rsquo;t Modify Frozen Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;FrozenError&lt;/code&gt; (also &lt;code&gt;RuntimeError: can't modify frozen&lt;/code&gt;) is raised when you try to modify a frozen object. In Ruby 3.2+, this is a dedicated exception class.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Frozen objects are immutable — you cannot change their contents. Attempting to modify a frozen string, array, hash, or any object raises &lt;code&gt;FrozenError&lt;/code&gt;. Freezing is used for thread safety and data integrity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frozen string modification&lt;/strong&gt; — appending to a frozen string.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frozen array modification&lt;/strong&gt; — pushing to a frozen array.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frozen hash modification&lt;/strong&gt; — adding keys to a frozen hash.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;String literals frozen by default&lt;/strong&gt; — Ruby 3.0+ with &lt;code&gt;# frozen_string_literal: true&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 1: Modifying a frozen string&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError: can&amp;#39;t modify frozen String&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 2: Modifying a frozen array&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;].&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;push(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError: can&amp;#39;t modify frozen Array&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 3: Modifying a frozen hash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; }&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;hash&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:b&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError: can&amp;#39;t modify frozen Hash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 4: String literals frozen by default (Ruby 3.0+)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# frozen_string_literal: true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use--to-create-unfrozen-copy"&gt;Fix 1: Use + to create unfrozen copy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;new_str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Creates a new unfrozen string&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-gsub-or-sub-for-string-modification"&gt;Fix 2: Use gsub or sub for string modification&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;sub!(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;h&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;H&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;new_str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; str&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;sub(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;h&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;H&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Returns a new string&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-create-mutable-copies-of-frozen-collections"&gt;Fix 3: Create mutable copies of frozen collections&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;].&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;push(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;].&lt;/span&gt;freeze
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;new_arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;dup
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;new_arr&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;push(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Works&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Or use + for arrays&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;new_arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; arr &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-use-stringnew-for-mutable-strings"&gt;Fix 4: Use String.new for mutable strings&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong — frozen string literal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# frozen_string_literal: true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FrozenError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct — explicitly create mutable string&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; String&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;new(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;str &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Works&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="runtime-error"&gt;RuntimeError&lt;/a&gt; — generic runtime error (parent for FrozenError in older Ruby).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="type-error"&gt;TypeError&lt;/a&gt; — wrong type for operation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="argument-error"&gt;ArgumentError&lt;/a&gt; — wrong number of arguments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>